POE-Component-Log4perl version 0.02
===================================

This module provides a simplified interface to the Log::Log4perl logging
module.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  POE
  Log::Log4perl

